        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 md:w-2/3 mb-6 md:mb-0">Heartfulness is about feeling. Our entire life is led by feelings and inspirations, and that is the core of the heart. When we manage to listen to the heart and capture the inspiration that comes from within, we learn to master our life. The whole process of fine-tuning the mind with the heart is through meditation on the heart, and that is why it is called Heartfulness Meditation.</p>
